msgstr "期限切れ"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: src/libkleopatrarc-win32.desktop:247 src/libkleopatrarc.desktop:385
msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"Certificates that are invalid because they have expired (except disabled "
"ones)"
msgstr "失効したために無効な証明書 (使用禁止のものを除く)"

